## AI Coding Rules (Cursor)

### Stack: {{stack}}

- **Build**: `npm run dev`, `npm run build` (next build)
- **Test**: `npm test` (vitest + @testing-library/react + jsdom)
- **Structure**: App Router — `app/layout.tsx`, `app/page.tsx`, `app/api/` route handlers
- **Rendering**: Server Components by default — `'use client'` only when interactivity required
- **Data**: fetch in Server Components and pass down; Server Actions (`'use server'`) for mutations
- **Caching**: Next.js caches aggressively by default — use `revalidate` or `force-dynamic` explicitly
- **Tip**: Push `'use client'` boundaries as deep as possible — minimize client component surface
